description: FIGHT FIRE WITH FIRE. FIGHT EVIL WITH SCIENCE! Collecting the never before reprinted Science Dog back-up story from INVINCIBLE #75, as well as the ALL-NEW full-length, never-before-seen conclusion of the story! This story has been years in the making-don't miss its epic conclusion!

What's better: an ugly reality or beautiful fantasy? This is the question the Doctor is forced to confront in a medieval fantasy world where Amy finds herself reluctantly cast as a damsel in distress.
name: A Fairytale Life, Part 2

description: Includes the Best American Comics selection, 'Turtle Keep it Steady,' plus several new stories. Juxtaposing an economy of line with sophisticated, unusual narratives, this is the long-awaited debut of an artist many are watching with interest.
name: I Will Bite You and Other Stories GN

volume.name: I Will Bite You and Other Stories

description: Because you demanded it, the wait is finally over – it's the all-Kroc issue! Ever wonder if you're doing things the right way or the wrong way? How about the Kroc way? This issue is filled with household, how-to, and cooking tips – the Kroc way! Don't worry, the Tiny Titans will be there, too!
name: The Kroc Issue!

description:
Collecting

  • CLASSIC X-MEN #43
  • BIZARRE ADVENTURES #27
  • PHOENIX: THE UNTOLD STORY WHAT IF? (1977)
  • #27 X-MEN #129-138
name: HC

description: A feral beast wanders in the night hunting for criminals, an animal with the strength and speed of a tiger. But what lies behind this night avenger? A spell, a folly or a crazy dream of justice?
name: Il sogno della tigre

description: A midsummer night's nightmare takes place in the old ruins of Stonehenge. Young Vicky Connely has witnessed a doomed rite with hood figures and human sacrifices, and therefore must die. A story hard to believe even for Dylan, but who if not him can help the girl?
name: Incubo di una notte di mezza estate

description: In a house suspended on the edge of a clif, two aged sisters tied together by a bloody phantom and a murder. Dylan has to sift through a tangle of lies and betrayals, and that which flows between the fingers is a powder charge of ghosts ...
name: La scogliera degli spettri

description: You see warrior seem to transverse to another reality where he runs around spouting  riddles mostly and fighting things.  the last few pages you are shown he is actually in a hospital bed and appears to be in a coma  possibly seriously injured.

A woman is targeted by a covert group of assassins! It's Robin, Kid Flash and Aqualad to the rescue, but can they save her from the combined menace of Hook and Black Spider? Only if they can escape from the deadly duo themselves! The junior heroes must prove they can work as a team and take on the menace of the League of Shadows at the same time!
name: By Hook Or By Web

description:
Collects GI Joe (1982-1994 Marvel) #101-110.

CLASSIC G.I. JOE VOL. 11 continues the original run of A REAL AMERICAN HERO, featuring stories like "The New Guard," "Amazing the Welkin," "Hero of the People," and "Apparent Conclusions."
name: Volume 11

description: What is the mystery that the ancient sage Uskebasi met , seeking for the meaning of life?  There are things that would be better not to know, but there is aways somebody who can't resist the power of curiosity.
name: Il signore del silenzio

description: On the pages of a newspaper never written, Dylan reads about some facts that have yet to happen, premonitions of a future yet to come. Is it a bad joke, or the course of time has really cracked?
name: Accadde domani

description: A very nice night club in London is maintained from beautiful Amber Cat: Nice music, pleasant company and something truly demonic: To prevent Apocalypse Dylan has to travel to the other side of the world in search of the Doors of Hell
name: Golconda!

description: A disfigured body lies on rotten leaves of the forest , surrounded by an eternal fog. Is it a hunting accident or a premeditated murder? To solve the case, Dylan will have to listen to the forest whispers, and one among them: the voice of the victim.
name: Una voce dal nulla
I giorni della morte e della speranza

description: First appearance of the Action Force strip.
name: Battle 422
